definition:
A woman living at the time of Divided Monarchy, first mentioned at 1Ki.22.42; 
 daughter of: Shilhi (H7977); married to Asa (H0609); 
 mother of: Jehoshaphat (H3092I)
 § Azubah = "forsaken"
1) wife of Caleb, the son of Hezron
2) daughter of Shilhi, wife of king Asa, and mother of king Jehoshaphat of Judah
